1
00:00:00,303 --> 00:00:03,134
This is the room where they used to hide me

2
00:00:03,877 --> 00:00:08,405
Where they used to hide me, and I was shackled
with a chain. There was a door here

3
00:00:09,013 --> 00:00:12,810
Before, there was a door here, and here
was a door. They had locked me in

4
00:00:13,370 --> 00:00:18,175
Because of how strict they were, there were three doors,
one door, this second one, and this third door

5
00:00:18,660 --> 00:00:25,222
We were here, shackled with chains,
and there were iron bars here that they had placed

6
00:00:26,132 --> 00:00:28,538
Here were iron bars that they had placed

7
00:00:30,079 --> 00:00:33,619
We were chained up. The chain was here

8
00:00:34,040 --> 00:00:36,446
The seven of us would sleep in this area

9
00:00:36,829 --> 00:00:40,120
Here, there used to be iron bars shaped like this

10
00:00:41,060 --> 00:00:45,158
At this same height, there were
iron bars. I would take off my clothes

11
00:00:45,258 --> 00:00:47,633
And rub my body with <i>ludaelin</i> [dish soap], and climb up

12
00:00:47,934 --> 00:00:50,707
There were pipes here. I would sit on them and squeeze myself through

13
00:00:51,701 --> 00:00:57,253
There was a hole over there, with
green pipes, pipes for the water heater

14
00:00:57,655 --> 00:01:01,142
I would talk to my wife and son. My wife and son came

15
00:01:01,863 --> 00:01:04,153
After I sent for her, my wife and son came

16
00:01:04,667 --> 00:01:06,931
I started talking to her. There was a metal ladder under the neighbors

17
00:01:07,023 --> 00:01:14,039
This area, they used it as a bathroom,
this thing here, they used it as a bathroom

18
00:01:14,652 --> 00:01:17,737
We never bathed because we were shackled in chains

19
00:01:18,078 --> 00:01:21,727
This bathroom was only a bathroom in name because we were shackled in chains

20
00:01:21,912 --> 00:01:26,814
From here I would look at the street
and at my wife. Sometimes they would sit here

21
00:01:27,209 --> 00:01:31,896
From here, we pierced the wall. I would climb up using a plastic container

22
00:01:32,369 --> 00:01:36,281
I would stand on a plastic container, look through like this, and I could see

23
00:01:36,710 --> 00:01:41,685
Now if you point the camera from here,
I can see my aunt Najah's house

24
00:01:42,088 --> 00:01:45,277
And how I could see my house from the east side

25
00:01:58,812 --> 00:02:02,139
Here you can see my aunt Najah's kitchen on the right, and the rooms on the left

26
00:02:02,233 --> 00:02:07,349
Whoever enters between the kitchen and the rooms is visible to us. We were from here

27
00:02:07,733 --> 00:02:11,583
We would signal to them from here, communicating by gestures. We had no other way

28
00:02:11,642 --> 00:02:16,001
This was their bathroom, and this was the chain

29
00:02:16,075 --> 00:02:20,339
The problem was not here. The chain was tied here

30
00:02:20,492 --> 00:02:23,946
We were seven people. Seven of us slept here, and I slept here

31
00:02:25,029 --> 00:02:30,332
Ibrahim al-Bariwi slept next to me here, and Ibrahim al-Alkan slept here

32
00:02:30,778 --> 00:02:36,268
Bara al-Hano was here, and Ibrahim al-Ayyoub here,
and Ramadan al-Jassim slept here

33
00:02:36,481 --> 00:02:39,694
Sometimes Ibrahim al-Ayyoub would sleep in Ibrahim al-Jassim's spot

34
00:02:40,162 --> 00:02:44,413
Then Shantar would come, that was Ibrahim al-Ayyoub's nickname. He slept

35
00:02:44,906 --> 00:02:50,426
These are the marks from the iron bars. Look at
the ceiling, the bars were placed here

36
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:53,840
On the ledge from this side. Those are their traces

37
00:02:54,533 --> 00:02:57,477
Everything you have seen here is factual evidence

38
00:02:58,031 --> 00:03:02,572
Look here at the traces of the iron bars
above, on the wall and on the ceiling here

39
00:03:02,733 --> 00:03:07,688
I would undress because my body was
so thin that my hands would slip out of the cuffs

40
00:03:07,868 --> 00:03:11,175
And rub my body with dish soap
just to be able to see my family

41
00:03:11,641 --> 00:03:14,627
And talk to them, and let them know I was still alive

42
00:03:15,077 --> 00:03:22,380
I stayed here for about two months, two months or a little more
